{"tid":1337377,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「721」學術分析遊行發展方向及建議","createTime":"2019-07-21T09:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T09:34:22.000Z","uid":58425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"acaea53332148a6abfe271acbd59ad81d13b54e4","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:12:40.000Z","msg":"以下只為學術討論，討論要點為香城online可以發展方向，<span style=\"color: red;\">本人並不鼓勵現實市民犯法，請勿誤會。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>分析：</strong><br />\n1.  警方表面䇿略係防止政府機關受衝擊<br />\n<br />\n2. 因此<em>警方想</em>遊行人士向銅鑼灣方向離開<br />\n<br />\n3. 縮短路線係為左減少單一時間聚集人數<br />\n<br />\n4. 民陣係和理非嘅組織，唔可以指望佢地指揮人群聚集<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>建議：</strong><br />\n0. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請開即時地圖實況</span></span>，以便了解我地優勢同可以做嘅事同去嘅地方 <br />\n<a href=\"https://103.hk/map/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F103.hk%2Fmap%2F&d=4cEDjPrkdumF5Vl7%2FlTecmztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=0a9be03a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://103.hk/map/</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 612打後嘅經驗，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要盡早行動</span></span></span>，7點後和理非開始少，12點大部份都會走<br />\n<br />\n2.利用人數優勢，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反包圍警察</span></span>。人群聚集實況請睇上面嘅網站。<br />\n<br />\n3. 承接1.,若要成功， <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">現場必需要有人指示人群去邊</span></span>。不可以要求民陣指揮。如果做唔到，我地最大嘅優勢，人數，就會消失。<br />\n<br />\n4. 承接2., 要有行動，其一方向係趁依家有人數時從中環金鐘<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反包圍金鐘同中環</span></span>，否則只會重蹈覆轍。<br />\n<br />\n5.記住各人有自己嘅底線，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔可以逼和理非犯法</span></span>，但可以利用佢地作保護。"},{"pid":"a9e08bac43ed6eed0e95074db2b77b4f6574a913","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」"},{"pid":"45a5d82bfd2120c1dabb55f8d9aaf98bf6a0757f","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:15:29.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」"},{"pid":"b48ecc27f03803901cd0411b0e9651e772faec47","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:17:11.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」<br />\n<br />\n補充，唔係叫人圍政總，但至少要反包圍到，可以終審法院，可以去西環，都可以圍政總。"},{"pid":"92e232f02a24eedfa156a3f2f76231caa2c48184","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」"},{"pid":"2103920e6809dd6c18f9f68bf272aa55a2f36689","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:18:03.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」"},{"pid":"89b9f0e470628186bd78be3b459a58c188f08025","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:18:50.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」"},{"pid":"6192a998182d261ba9171834ba2ced710de70387","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:19:26.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」"},{"pid":"0abf81bc2c2f8c44b2eb01e1f21721372b4f9946","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:19:44.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」"},{"pid":"a6be9363e2bf4f7e2ea96bf555791e5c42e19b4a","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:19:54.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」"},{"pid":"9a77f06a944d3a8b85b582ca67f8a2419499ee09","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:20:07.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」"},{"pid":"bf23bcb2b2a8100df144b52d52dd38c33f2d1056","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:20:24.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」"},{"pid":"eeb3f7041f6091f03cb11e3735b2d66e857d8a18","tid":1337377,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"有冇其他「分析撚」"},{"pid":"73dca5ef2253e27f755d3824c232920e0580781e","tid":1337377,"uid":58